# Ablation Phases

Structure code sequentially under `src/fedmaq/`:

| Phase | Package | Goal |
| ----- | ------- | ---- |
| 1 | `phase1_env/` | PyTorch/Flower env, vision datasets, Dirichlet non-IID, bandwidth stragglers |
| 2 | `phase2_quant/` | Isolate resource/data/time-aware uplink quantization vs static baselines |
| 3 | `phase3_kd/` | Server-side logit/feature KD to recover accuracy from quantization noise |
| 4 | `phase4_benchmark/` | Unified FedMAQ vs SOTA across datasets |

Do not skip phases when adding features. Baselines live in `baselines/`, not separate top-level reproduction folders.
